body:
I cannot compile this file if I neither `using ::tensorflow::int32;` nor change `int32` to `int32_t`.

My environment is OSX 10.12.6 with clang++ version "900.0.39.2". The test is executed by:

```shell
bazel test -s -c dbg //tensorflow/contrib/lite/kernels:gather_test
```

Can you help verify this? Thanks.
